com.yandex.money.api.net.clients

Interface ApiClient

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultApiClient

    public interface ApiClient
    Yandex.Money API client. The purpose of this interface is to provide methods to execute API functions, get resources from server and help with user's authorization.
